caption.title: Melting curve analysis of the second PCR.
caption.p: A—Melting curve analysis at 0.4°C step size, B—Melting curve analysis at 0.1°C step size, C—Temperature range of the melting peaks at 0.1°C step size. The colour codes in the first two graphs were Red—DENV-1, Dark Blue—DENV-2, Yellow—DENV-3, Black—DENV-4 respectively.
